really is quite tasty.

00:20:12.128 --> 00:20:14.506 position:50% align:center
It's the connection
that's so important.

00:20:14.589 --> 00:20:17.384 position:50% align:center
Even if the flavor is still the
same, the experience isn't

00:20:17.467 --> 00:20:20.970 position:50% align:center
because Rosemary wasn't the one
who lovingly stomped the grapes.

00:20:21.054 --> 00:20:22.389 position:50% align:center
Don't you see.

