00:20:53.920 --> 00:20:55.171 position:50% align:center
Now, let me see.

00:20:55.255 --> 00:20:56.881 position:50% align:center
Yes, here we go!

00:21:00.135 --> 00:21:03.346 position:50% align:center
[ELAINA giggling]

00:21:06.349 --> 00:21:10.687 position:50% align:center
[ALL screaming]

00:21:10.770 --> 00:21:13.231 position:50% align:center
[laughing]

00:21:14.816 --> 00:21:15.608 position:50% align:center
[BOY 07A]
And then?

00:21:15.692 --> 00:21:17.736 position:50% align:center
What happened after that?

00:21:17.819 --> 00:21:18.987 position:50% align:center
[THIS VILLAGE CHIEF 07A]
Those grape pellets

00:21:19.070 --> 00:21:21.322 position:50% align:center
hit every last one of us.

00:21:24.367 --> 00:21:27.162 position:50% align:center
[THIS VILLAGE CHIEF 07A]
We were all knocked out.

00:21:27.245 --> 00:21:30.373 position:50% align:center
And when we finally
came to, we discovered

00:21:30.457 --> 00:21:32.834 position:50% align:center
that the witch had already left.

00:21:34.794 --> 00:21:36.212 position:50% align:center
Oh...

00:21:42.761 --> 00:21:44.012 position:50% align:center
[THIS VILLAGE CHIEF 07A]
And that's the story

00:21:44.095 --> 00:21:46.348 position:50% align:center
of how the Grape-Throwing
Festival began.

00:21:46.431 --> 00:21:48.683 position:50% align:center
Turned out it was a good
way to release stress.

00:21:48.767 --> 00:21:50.852 position:50% align:center
So it became a tradition
we celebrated

00:21:50.935 --> 00:21:53.188 position:50% align:center
during harvest time
every single year.

00:21:53.271 --> 00:21:54.981 position:50% align:center
Before we knew it,
the two villages

00:21:55.065 --> 00:21:57.400 position:50% align:center
set aside their differences
and united as one.

00:21:57.484 --> 00:21:58.943 position:50% align:center
[BOY 07A]
Wow.

00:21:59.027 --> 00:22:01.529 position:50% align:center
That nice witch really helped
us out, didn't she, Grandpa?

00:22:01.613 --> 00:22:03.656 position:50% align:center
Yes, she sure did.

00:22:07.535 --> 00:22:09.621 position:50% align:center
[BOY 07A]
