How 'bout you go and wash up.

00:22:20.507 --> 00:22:21.800 position:50% align:center
Okay!

00:22:22.884 --> 00:22:26.137 position:50% align:center
Ripening over the years
into something truly amazing,

00:22:26.221 --> 00:22:30.100 position:50% align:center
and still tempting me
no matter how old.

00:22:30.183 --> 00:22:33.770 position:50% align:center
Hey. You deserve a break.
How about some lunch?

00:22:33.853 --> 00:22:35.188 position:50% align:center
